ene glycol varying concentration\n(7.5-20wt%) modelled by Khandavalli, et al.[1]. The simulations were carried\nout for low generalized Reynolds numbers, corresponding to the shear thickening\nregion of the shear viscosity curve for each formulation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 May 2023 09:53:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-10"}
